# Force LF on checkout everywhere (incl. Windows CI): source-contract tests
# match exact source text and have twice been broken by CRLF materialization
# (v1.5.0 model-pill CSS regexes, v1.6.0 skill/runner contracts).
* text=auto eol=lf
# PowerShell prefers CRLF.
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
# Binaries.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
